{"html":"<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1080px;height:1350px;background:#0D0D0D;display:flex;flex-direction:column;position:relative;overflow:hidden;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif}.yellow-bar{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:10px;background:#F4C000}.bg-number{position:absolute;right:-30px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-60%);font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:420px;color:rgba(244,192,0,0.04);line-height:1}.glow{position:absolute;width:600px;height:600px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,80,0,0.10) 0%,transparent 70%);top:100px;left:200px}.main{position:relative;z-index:3;padding:120px 80px 80px 100px;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}.step-tag{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-bottom:48px}.step-num{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:80px;color:#F4C000;line-height:1}.step-label{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}.step-word{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)}.step-name{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.headline{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:96px;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.0;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:40px}.headline .accent{color:#F4C000}.divider{width:60px;height:4px;background:#F4C000;margin-bottom:40px}.body-text{font-size:26px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);line-height:1.7;max-width:820px;margin-bottom:40px}.body-text strong{color:#F4C000;font-weight:600}.metrics{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-top:8px}.metric{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-top:3px solid #F4C000;padding:28px 22px}.m-stat{font-family:Anton,sans-serif;font-size:64px;color:#F4C000;line-height:1;margin-bottom:8px}.m-label{font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:1.4}.logo{position:absolute;bottom:56px;right:72px;width:64px;opacity:0.5;z-index:4}.step-indicator{position:absolute;bottom:60px;left:100px;display:flex;gap:8px;z-index:4}.dot{width:28px;height:4px;background:#F4C000;border-radius:2px}.dot-inactive{width:12px;height:4px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:2px}</style><div class=\"slide\"><div class=\"yellow-bar\"></div><div class=\"bg-number\">04</div><div class=\"glow\"></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"step-tag\"><div class=\"step-num\">04</div><div class=\"step-label\"><span class=\"step-word\">Efecto</span><span class=\"step-name\">Menos vida &uacute;til</span></div></div><div class=\"headline\">El calor<br>acorta<br><span class=\"accent\">su vida.</span></div><div class=\"divider\"></div><div class=\"body-text\">Cada componente tiene un l&iacute;mite t&eacute;rmico. El calor sostenido <strong>degrada chips, soldaduras y bater&iacute;a</strong>. Una PC caliente envejece <strong>3 veces m&aacute;s r&aacute;pido</strong>.</div><div class=\"metrics\"><div class=\"metric\"><div class=\"m-stat\">-50%</div><div class=\"m-label\">Vida &uacute;til del SSD</div></div><div class=\"metric\"><div class=\"m-stat\">-40%</div><div class=\"m-label\">Capacidad de bater&iacute;a</div></div><div class=\"metric\"><div class=\"m-stat\">2x</div><div class=\"m-label\">Riesgo de falla del CPU</div></div></div></div><img class=\"logo\" src=\"/uploads/64d70ecd-3300-4ef3-b614-7839245e41fb.png\" /><div class=\"step-indicator\"><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div><div class=\"dot\"></div><div class=\"dot-inactive\"></div></div></div>","notes":"Slide 5: Menos vida útil — Métricas de degradación"}
